data.description: Sellers are motivated! Welcome HOME!!! Nestled In Timber Ridge with no HOA, this Absolutely BEAUTIFUL Country Home is now on the market to be yours!!! Spacious doesn't even come close to describing the size of each room. This open layout floorplan is not like anything you have seen. This home has held weddings, gatherings, and has been loved greatly. The spacious living room has a built-in fireplace perfect for pictures and holidays. Perfect for while you work, talk, or gather to make memories. The kitchen has an amazing granite/ oak island that wraps around, so you'll always have your family or friends feel welcomed to join you while you cook or just catch up. The outdoor patio also has ample space for gatherings. Walking into the hallway will lead you to the first bedroom. The first bedroom boast excitement as it has a built-in vanity, with a working sink, a walk-in closet, and plenty of room to do whatever you want to do. The second bedroom has plenty of space, and TWO closets!!! While the bathroom across the hall has a layout to give you the most comfort. Walking to the furthest point you'll find the MASTER Bedroom of all bedrooms. This ENORMOUS room has a master bathroom suite. With MULTIPLE French doors leading to the Spacious Lanai. LET ME ADD!! There is a laundry chute leading to the laundry room. GOODBYE HAMPERS!!!   The Laundry room also has granite and a laundry tub!! This country home has a city location with a detached, also very spacious garage with a workshop, and is connected to the home through a breeze way. This home is an absolute must see!!! Schedule your showing TODAY!!!
